# TALENT GROWTH INTEGRATED MASTER REBUILT

status: integrated-master-rebuilt
system: TalentGrowth
formal_name_ja: 人材成長支援・人材評価システム
formal_name_en: Talent Growth Support & Evaluation System
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

# 1. identity
TalentGrowth は、
人材の現在地と次行動を、
証拠付きで見える化し、
成長支援と会社評価をつなぐための統合設計である。

# 2. fixed support targets
- multilingual
- multi-currency
- iPhone
- Android
- PC
- tablet

# 3. users
- employee
- manager
- HR
- executive
- admin

# 4. fixed design pillars
- evidence-first
- role-fit first
- growth-action first
- explainability first
- approval / calibration / audit mandatory
- AI is assist only

# 5. integrated feature surface

## profile and evidence
- employee profile
- academics
- certifications
- skills
- career histories
- achievements
- evidence linkage

## evaluation and governance
- self review
- manager review
- HR review
- send back
- calibration
- approve
- publish
- reopen
- audit search

## growth and strategy
- gap analysis
- growth plan
- recommendations
- MBO linkage
- role-fit candidates
- promotion readiness
- successor candidates
- career simulation

## analytics and reporting
- dashboard KPIs
- distribution analytics
- evaluator bias analytics
- 9box
- training ROI
- exports

## operations and platform
- outbox
- notification
- batch / snapshot jobs
- RLS
- break-glass
- frontend state / cache / sync

# 6. score system summary
主要 score:
- total_evaluation_score
- current_role_fit_score
- target_role_fit_score
- growth_potential_score
- promotion_readiness_score
- successor_readiness_score

rank:
- S
- A
- B
- C
- D

rules:
- formula before calibration
- gate before rank
- mandatory missing items can cap score/rank
- current fit と future readiness は別評価

