# 10. security summary
- employee_self = self-centered
- manager = team-centered
- HR = company governance
- executive = aggregate-first
- admin = technical admin, not default raw evaluator
- break-glass = reason + time bound + audit

# 11. event and job summary
event flow:
- state change
- outbox append
- notification derive
- async delivery

batch / job flow:
- outbox publish
- notification deliver
- expiry scan
- evaluation snapshot
- role-fit refresh
- analytics refresh
- recommendation refresh
- export generate
- consistency checks

# 12. frontend summary
- server truth first
- selective offline
- no offline finalization
- visible sync status
- explicit conflict handling
- draft rescue for safe edit flows

